<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA5">
<l>peṟṟatāy nīyē piṟappitta tantainī</l>
<l>maṟṟaiyā rāvārum nīpēci leṟṟēyō</l>
<l>māyamā māyavaḷai māyamulai vāyvaitta</l>
<l>nīyamā kāṭṭum neṟi.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mother who got you, the father who begot you,</l>
<l>who else are they? If you speak, how is it</l>
<l>that you who, for the traitress great in treachery to perish,</l>
<l>put into [his] mouth [her] breast, father, show [us] the way?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
